accessibility.text: Reduced startup and shutdown time by +50%
Unique screenshot folder per application start
C-Troll application for remote application start
Added improved Earth WMS server from ESRI
Automatic fade-in of Digital Universe objects
Automatically recompute aspect ratio when window size changes
Spout input into screen and world space objects
QOL improvements for touch table interaction
Added ability to hide scene graph nodes in the UI
Support for fixed rotation and rapid prototyping
New Parallel Connection that can work without a dedicated server
